Quickstrike:




Quickstrike carried Black Arachnia to a lab room. He set her feet 
down on the ground, still with a grip on her. He looked at her with a 
nervous look on his face. "Say ya got uh pod wit' uh blank 
protoform." Otherwise he wouldn't know what to do with the offspring.
